<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_21_r2l5"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her <expan>haupt</expan> / vns hat furgelegt hans Ryeter </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_21_r2l6">der elter <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> Burger / vvie daʒ Jr ſein pürg ſeıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_21_r2l7">vmb neuncʒig <expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> / für <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> Marſchalken </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_21_r2l9"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> vettern </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_21_r2l8">pruder </ab></add> <expan>ſelıge<ex>n</ex></expan> / die Jm wol ſechs Jar auſʒenge = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_21_r2l11"><expan>ſtande<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_21_r2l10">ſein </ab></add> vnd niht becʒalt <expan>künne<ex>n</ex></expan> werden <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> etc daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_21_r2l12">Jr <expan>gedenke<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>beſtelle<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet / daʒ dem <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_21_r2l13"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> Burger <expan>dıeſelb</expan> ſein ſchulde noch <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒogenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_21_r2l16">gerıht vnd becʒalt 
<add><ab facs="#facs_21_r2l15">werde </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough">werde / vnd darümb vnkl </del> / Als etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_21_r2l17">das wöllen etc / <expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan> geſchehe des niht / So müſten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_21_r2l18">wir dem <expan>ſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> Burger geſtatten / vvie Er ew </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_21_r2l19">darcʒu breht eʒ wer mit <expan>geıſtliche<ex>n</ex></expan> oder <expan>werltlıhe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
